{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>學習記憶總是讓你感到頭疼嗎？《Flashcards Maker》這款創新的抽認卡應用，今天限時免費中，它能幫助你以極其直覺的方式掌握任何知識點。無論你是學生準備考試、學習新語言，還是專業人士需要記憶術語，都能透過它輕鬆提升學習效率，讓記憶不再是枯燥的負擔。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/460x460bb-75-27.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>直覺滑動手勢 高效記憶無負擔</h2>\n    <p>這款應用以獨特的滑動手勢設計，讓你左右輕掃即可快速分類卡片，告別繁瑣點擊。其極簡用戶界面搭配清晰排版與流暢動畫，專注於記憶。它更具備 100% 離線運作且無需帳戶的特性，讓你隨時隨地，即開即學，免除網絡束縛與隱私疑慮。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-44-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-45-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-46-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-47-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-48-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：Flashcards Maker: Swipe Study</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Utilities</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-05T12:31:02.462745+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":318,"images":6,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}